data.description: Adorable 3/2/2 in a wonderful neighborhood close to the park. Cathedral ceiling with brick fireplace in the living room, with Skylights.  Coffered Ceiling in Master and a beautiful walk in shower.  Workshop in the backyard has electricity.  This home is looking forward to it's new owners who are going to love it!  Make your appointment with your favorite realtor but hurry we are priced to sell quickly.!
